text: Barbara von Grebel-Schiendorfer (born 27 September 1950) is a Swiss equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zürich
